[
  {
    "text": "I am",
    "start": 0.48,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Proximo. I shall be closer to you for",
    "start": 1.96,
    "duration": 4.04
  },
  {
    "text": "the next few days, which will be the",
    "start": 4.48,
    "duration": 4.159
  },
  {
    "text": "last of your miserable lives than that",
    "start": 6.0,
    "duration": 4.24
  },
  {
    "text": "of a mother that brought you screaming",
    "start": 8.639,
    "duration": 3.841
  },
  {
    "text": "into this world.",
    "start": 10.24,
    "duration": 4.08
  },
  {
    "text": "I did not pay good money for you for",
    "start": 12.48,
    "duration": 3.48
  },
  {
    "text": "your",
    "start": 14.32,
    "duration": 4.08
  },
  {
    "text": "company. I paid it so that I could",
    "start": 15.96,
    "duration": 4.079
  },
  {
    "text": "profit from your",
    "start": 18.4,
    "duration": 5.2
  },
  {
    "text": "death. And as your mother was there at",
    "start": 20.039,
    "duration": 5.881
  },
  {
    "text": "your beginning,",
    "start": 23.6,
    "duration": 6.24
  },
  {
    "text": "so I should be there at your end.",
    "start": 25.92,
    "duration": 7.92
  },
  {
    "text": "And when you die, and die you shall,",
    "start": 29.84,
    "duration": 9.16
  },
  {
    "text": "your transition shall be to the sound of",
    "start": 33.84,
    "duration": 5.16
  },
  {
    "text": "gladiators. I salute you.",
    "start": 43.079,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Yellow.",
    "start": 55.039,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "[Applause]",
    "start": 65.04,
    "duration": 6.399
  },
  {
    "text": "Good.",
    "start": 69.6,
    "duration": 4.22
  },
  {
