    "duration": 6.69
  },
  {
    "text": "At the end. At the end.",
    "start": 177.68,
    "duration": 5.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you not",
    "start": 195.36,
    "duration": 6.04
  },
  {
    "text": "entertained? Are you not entertained?",
    "start": 196.599,
    "duration": 4.801
  },
  {
    "text": "Is this not why you are here?",
    "start": 201.76,
    "duration": 3.96
  },
  {
    "text": "[Applause]",
    "start": 210.01,
    "duration": 10.449
  },
  {
    "text": "Guys,",
    "start": 228.84,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "guys, Your fame is welld deserved.",
    "start": 238.76,
    "duration": 3.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Spveners, I don't think there's ever",
    "start": 241.36,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "been a gladiator to match you. As for",
    "start": 242.64,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "this young man, he insists you are",
    "start": 244.64,
    "duration": 4.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Hector reborn. Was a",
    "start": 245.92,
    "duration": 5.599
  },
  {
    "text": "Hercules. Why doesn't the hero reveal",
    "start": 249.56,
    "duration": 5.239
  },
  {
    "text": "himself and tell us all your real",
    "start": 251.519,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "name? You do have a name.",
    "start": 255.32,
    "duration": 7.12
  },
  {
    "text": "My name is Gladiator.",
    "start": 258.799,
    "duration": 3.641
  },
  {
    "text": "How dare you show your back to me,",
    "start": 263.919,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "slave?",
    "start": 266.32,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Will you remove your helmet and tell me",
    "start": 268.639,
    "duration": 4.921
  },
  {
    "text": "your name?",
    "start": 270.32,
    "duration": 3.24
  },
  {
    "text": "My name is Maximus Desimus Meridius,",
    "start": 283.6,
    "duration": 4.879
  },
  {
    "text": "commander of the armies of the north,",
    "start": 286.479,
    "duration": 3.561
  },
  {
    "text": "general of the Felix",
    "start": 288.479,
    "duration": 3.921
  },
  {
    "text": "Legions, loyal servant to the true",
    "start": 290.04,
    "duration": 4.719
  },
  {
    "text": "emperor, Marcus",
    "start": 292.4,
    "duration": 5.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Aurelius, father to a murdered son,",
    "start": 294.759,
    "duration": 5.201
  },
  {
    "text": "husband to a murdered",
    "start": 298.24,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "wife, and I will have my venyards in",
    "start": 299.96,
    "duration": 7.36
  },
  {
    "text": "this life or the next.",
    "start": 303.52,
    "duration": 3.8
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm",
    "start": 330.6,
    "duration": 2.76
  },
  {
