    "duration": 6.72
  },
  {
    "text": "men. Senator Graas is to be reinstated.",
    "start": 645.72,
    "duration": 6.72
  },
  {
    "text": "There was a dream that was",
    "start": 650.64,
    "duration": 4.439
  },
  {
    "text": "wrong. It shall be",
    "start": 652.44,
    "duration": 4.92
  },
  {
    "text": "realized. These are the wishes of Marcus",
    "start": 655.079,
    "duration": 4.521
